Name: Average time from SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion to SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Total time between Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation and SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Minimum time it takes SW-Checklist Completed to be done after Manuscript Export Succeeded
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Total waiting time to the SW-Checklist Completed following Plagiarism Originality Report Completed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Time from SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days to SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Average time it takes SW-Checklist Completed after Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Minimum time between Manuscript Export Succeeded and SW-Checklist Completed across all process variants
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Total resolution time of SW-Checklist Completed in cases that eventually lead to SW-EIC Accept
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completed' and activity 'SW-EIC Accept'

Name: Time of SW-Checklist Completed relative to the occurrence of Plagiarism Percent Match Threshold Exceeded
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Percent Match Threshold Exceeded' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Average time from SW-Checklist Completion now due to SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completion now due' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Minimum time it takes SW-Checklist Completed to occur after the first event in the case
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Elapsed time between Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation and SW-Checklist Completed in high-duration variants (performance > 1,000,000 seconds)
Metric: the average of the function base > 1000000 where base is the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and the last time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Average time for SW-Checklist Completed in cases where the subsequent activity is SW-Awaiting AE Assignment versus SW-Initial Reviewer Selection
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Time from Manuscript Export Succeeded to SW-Checklist Completed in variants involving repeated Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission events
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Total time until SW-Checklist Completed is performed in cases that later experience multiple reviewer assignment cycles (e.g., SW-AE Assign Reviewers appearing more than five times)
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Minimum time between Plagiarism Originality Report Completed and SW-Checklist Completed in variants that proceed directly to editor assignment without reminders
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Cycle Time of SW-Checklist Completed measured from the moment the manuscript enters the system (Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation) until checklist completion
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Average time for SW-Checklist Completed grouped by case:concept:name
Total time between SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and SW-Checklist Completed in variants ending with SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'begin': activity == 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion'", 'end': "activity == 'SW-Checklist Completed'", 'aggregation': 'total', 'filter': "activity == 'SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit'"}"
